<L>__{exterior colosseum arena day}
<A>__{the ending of a group fight proximo's gladiators triumphant. the crowd waits for the delicious act of defiance. we note many placard and banners honoring "maximus the merciful." maximus, vibius, juba and a few other gladiators toss down their weapons and walk off, leaving their opponents alive. the crowd roars. they have completely embraced maximus and his fellow gladiators. gracchus, in the stands, laughs. the drums finally conclude.}
